reviews.review_text: If only we had the master source .... I really appreciate this sound and effort by the tapers but this 1st generation tape suffers from the ages or corrosion.  If you carefully listen one can hear the the right channel suffer loss in EQ and presence as the tape reels.  I really enjoy the ME-80's which yield a very natural soundfield and accept high volume sound pressure levels but maybe if you listen Lo Fi from a jam box around a fire this maybe the best source ...
